I´m facing the same Problem

`$Servers | foreach-object -parallel {
$broker = "$_.domain.com"

Write-Host "Restarting now $broker" -ForegroundColor Green

try {
restart-computer -computername $broker -Force -ErrorAction Stop -Wait -For WinRM -Delay 2`}

The restart-computer is running endless...

For me it is looking that something is different with the restart-computer cmdlet as in Version 5.1

Will this being fixed?
